49;\">//第三个参数(</span>columns<span style=\"color:#494949;\">) 字段名称</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#494949;\">qw.orderBy(true, true, \"status\").orderBy(true, false, \"name\");</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#494949;\">SQL执行: select * from tab_name tb order by status asc , name desc;</span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n</div>\n</div>", "first_tag": "SQL", "cpp": 0, "csharp": 0, "python": 0, "javascript": 0, "java": 0, "sql": 1, "php": 0, "time": "2022-05-11 10:19:20", "summary": "提供的方法：使用第一个方法实现多字段自定义排序：第一个参数是否将该条件加入到第二个参数是否升序排列，，第三个参数字段名称执行"}